Yin swings her whip 1350 units to pull herself to a target or the world;
If the Target is an Enemy, she deals 100/<wbr>145/<wbr>190/<wbr>235/<wbr>280 <AttackDamageText>(+140%</AttackDamageText><img id="ADIconOrange"></img><AttackDamageText>)</AttackDamageText> physical damage, Slows them by 90% for 0.2s, and generates 3 stacks of Rising Storm.
She then leaps in a direction of her choice.
